      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615011313,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Dissecting Rate Limiter",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Dissecting Rate Limiter",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HoG4pjTFnt_iwTq4xfdnh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1489.417714049791,
      "y": 6638.657272388805,
      "width": 715,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b40",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 238461948,
      "version": 363,
      "versionNonce": 1675018139,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615011313,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Rate limiter need to track #requests in a given period\nHence we need a database to hold the count, but which one?\n\n1. For every incoming request, we would update the DB.\n2. For every incoming request, we would read from db (aggregate).\n3. We need ability to \"clock\" the time.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rate limiter need to track #requests in a given period\nHence we need a database to hold the count, but which one?\n\n1. For every incoming request, we would update the DB.\n2. For every incoming request, we would read from db (aggregate).\n3. We need ability to \"clock\" the time.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zj3vx6stBSi_Mkqac0i-q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1488.3429514111199,
      "y": 6837.967884156796,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b41",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1888688764,
      "version": 31,
      "versionNonce": 2041240469,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615011313,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Say, we rate limit per user",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Say, we rate limit per user",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-qc6xIwH_cOm9SL-SLAK2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1485.4461302365762,
      "y": 6887.213844124036,
      "width": 528,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b42",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1862150780,
      "version": 178,
      "versionNonce": 1873941563,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615011313,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. we store #request in current period.\n2. Once the period is over we reset the counter.\n\n\nResetting the count == expiring the key\n\nKV STORE + EXPIRATION == REDIS",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. we store #request in current period.\n2. Once the period is over we reset the counter.\n\n\nResetting the count == expiring the key\n\nKV STORE + EXPIRATION == REDIS",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
