      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. We expose service (HTTP endpoint) that talks to rate limiter database.\n2. We let the service directly talk to rate limiter DB\n    - Saves one network hop\n    - But exposes critical internal details ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. We expose service (HTTP endpoint) that talks to rate limiter database.\n2. We let the service directly talk to rate limiter DB\n    - Saves one network hop\n    - But exposes critical internal details ",
