      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615016727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Scaling Rate limiter",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Scaling Rate limiter",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BpOUSzzZm2BBETvFYCBt6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1509.470780415642,
      "y": 8871.651305350939,
      "width": 737,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5X",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 133233404,
      "version": 125,
      "versionNonce": 566830133,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615020789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Given the service are directly talking to the Rate Limiter Database\nScaling rate limiter = Scaling the database",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Given the service are directly talking to the Rate Limiter Database\nScaling rate limiter = Scaling the database",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "O7uU9DXD3ii0GT5FTQpD1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1515.8869231548567,
      "y": 8973.442172888814,
      "width": 704,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 526916,
      "version": 273,
      "versionNonce": 368190875,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615020789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Should we scale Vertically ? -> YES\n- Should we add read replicas? -> No!! Traffic is not read heavy\n- Should we shard the database? -> YES ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Should we scale Vertically ? -> YES\n- Should we add read replicas? -> No!! Traffic is not read heavy\n- Should we shard the database? -> YES ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ypNYpZebnP4u4-176F0CP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1550.5141280135458,
      "y": 9061.571066926874,
      "width": 473,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 296241020,
      "version": 130,
      "versionNonce": 367056277,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615020789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "any funtion in backend service will extract\n - user_id from token\n - check rate limiter DB\n - If good, then proceed.\n - Otherwise block",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "any funtion in backend service will extract\n - user_id from token\n - check rate limiter DB\n - If good, then proceed.\n - Otherwise block",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QhPemc9SFYdUM0fuuOUBc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2075.643542517407,
      "y": 9080.994781346219,
      "width": 330,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 99654780,
      "version": 136,
      "versionNonce": 1433451067,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615020789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Note: the access is key based\n    - user_id -> count (4 + 4)\n    - ip -> count (16 + 4)\n    - token -> count (16 + 4)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Note: the access is key based\n    - user_id -> count (4 + 4)\n    - ip -> count (16 + 4)\n    - token -> count (16 + 4)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "b6phBtNRF2VNRZuCuZdw5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1493.418237003106,
      "y": 9261.06479390048,
      "width": 935,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 312208068,
      "version": 166,
      "versionNonce": 45832949,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775615020789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Hence we can easily shard the database to handle more load, FIG 1.3 shows SHARD REDIS",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hence we can easily shard the database to handle more load, FIG 1.3 shows SHARD REDIS",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
