      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775613376931,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Some notifications are more important than other\ne.g. Appointment Reminde >>> Marketing push",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Some notifications are more important than other\ne.g. Appointment Reminde >>> Marketing push",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SZF6_5VlhnuhrKcGy6VQo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1486.9973949347352,
      "y": 18250.345869665623,
      "width": 836,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 203593179,
      "version": 309,
      "versionNonce": 1702127925,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775613379121,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In our current architecture, one marketing campaign will keep executors busy\nand all other notifications will strave in the Queue.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In our current architecture, one marketing campaign will keep executors busy\nand all other notifications will strave in the Queue.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8lzznAM-QtXlB5ePke1Zk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1490.8530057162095,
      "y": 18327.63727233463,
      "width": 1023,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9k",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 359469691,
      "version": 169,
      "versionNonce": 1249507355,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775613496220,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "To solve this: instead of having one notificaion emitter queue, have multiple - priority wise\n(P1, P2, P3) and each having it's own set of workers, FIG 1.5",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To solve this: instead of having one notificaion emitter queue, have multiple - priority wise\n(P1, P2, P3) and each having it's own set of workers, FIG 1.5",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
