      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775614764898,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Notification Tracker DB\n- Light weight and shard-table.\n- In memory with periodic persistence\n- Bloom Filter support a a plus. (Space Efficient)\n\nSo Redis support all the 3 requriement, hence we go with redis here.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Notification Tracker DB\n- Light weight and shard-table.\n- In memory with periodic persistence\n- Bloom Filter support a a plus. (Space Efficient)\n\nSo Redis support all the 3 requriement, hence we go with redis here.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
